Package: NNRCM
Type: Package
Title: Spatial inference and predictions using the univariate and bivariate nearest-neighbor
    gaussian process with random covariance matrix (NN-RCM).
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-11-09
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Isabelle",
           family = "Grenier",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "igrenier@ucsc.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Maintainer: Isabelle Grenier <igrenier@ucsc.edu>
Description: This package implements the non-stationary and non-isotropic spatial 
    model NN-RCM. Both the univariate and bivariate versions are available. The package
    allows for the MCMC version as well as the marginal maximization version
    which is faster for large spatial datasets.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: Rcpp (>= 1.0.5), spNNGP (>= 0.1.5), RcppArmadillo, RcppParallel, dplyr,
    fields, ggplot2, RandomFields, geoR, MASS, spBayes, MCMCpack, RConics, doParallel,
    mvtnorm
LinkingTo: Rcpp, RcppArmadillo, RcppParallel, BH
Encoding: UTF-8
